sick slider!

sizeable image slider using jquery
packed up in a middleman project

next/prev buttons
autorotation
pause on hover (or any other event)

not that special but it works!

start like that:

$(document).ready ->
  slider = new SickSlider()
  
  
possible options:

  autoloop:     true/false    default: true                       - automatically shifts pictures
  cicle:        true/false    default: true                       - create an infinite loop last to first
  transition:   time in ms    default: 1000                       - time given to run the fadein/fadeout effect
  interval:     time in ms    default: 4000                       - display time of every picture (not needed if autoloop = false)
  images:       image array   default: $("#gallery img")          - divID containing the img's (see index.html file)
  
  
have fun